Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链金术是将物质理解分解并且再构筑的科学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不是万能的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不能从无中诞生物质
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须付出相应的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就是链金术的基本 等价交换
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链金术师有一个禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是人体链成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是任何人都不能侵犯的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马斯·休斯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被身上纹了咬尾蛇刺青的神秘人物杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马斯坦古对这一血案怀有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了这件事和军队上层部有关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次决意进入中央
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不知道的爱德和阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与温莉一起向着师傅所在的城市达普利斯前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着南部开始了旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}拉修巴雷的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉修巴雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛斯的11年式造型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到有一天能亲眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是机械铠的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没理由非得在这大热天里观赏机械铠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下温莉早点去达普利斯就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟 打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个机械铠的形状很稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦 大家也都来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下 住手 住…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 那里 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都热心于研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 所以才说机械铠技师这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家链金术师的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是帕妮娘干的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专找观光客下手的小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那家伙现在在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 相对地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我们看一下小哥的机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在一个叫多明尼克的机械铠技师那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说为了能采掘优质的矿石而住在深山里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路真的是对的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会被骗了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追根究底 还不是因为你想去那个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银怀表被偷是因为你自己不注意吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 你们俩看下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会到处躲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 呼吸变急促了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 还给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西在这里并不稀奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左脚是1.5英吋加尔巴林炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来抓我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会让你逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别放她走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 绝对不放开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,750)}（捏紧）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在让我仔细看清楚之前是绝对不放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 请放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种机械铠 第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说悬挂装置也很高级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎么看 这个全体的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这没有多余的设计
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我的银怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做出这种机械铠 我真的很佩服你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这个不是我制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得有点重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给装备者加上负担可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这小子才那么矮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说我矮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 弄得再轻一点的话 我的身高也会长高？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 好高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高好高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真矮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多明尼克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收我为弟子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微想一想也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 我不收弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就教她如何做出能让我长高的机械铠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 爸爸很顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水蚤 水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 是小宝宝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能摸摸你的肚子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以前也像这样呆在妈妈的肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气不好 关节就痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么装上了机械铠？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被卷进列车事故
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双亲都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有可以依靠的人 再加上不能走路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像是世界末日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那个时候 遇到了多明尼克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副自己是这个世上最不幸的人似的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人最让人生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开 放开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我的表情一定很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 莫名其妙地就被装上了机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手术痛死了 恢复训练辛苦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用双脚站在大地上的时候 我非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很感谢多明尼克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算花费一生来报答他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还一次都没有收过我钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才 偷窃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要感谢他的话 就不要再偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个双脚是多明尼克先生的诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你也必须用诚意来报答他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要用一生来报答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要偷窃 实实在在地站起来工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你那双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样 多明尼克先生也一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏踏实实地工作来还这个情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 要去还了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 难道弄坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖子打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是用链金术把盖子盖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是显然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为里面有被看到了就会很害臊的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看爱德的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“别忘了 11年10月3日”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个还给爱德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求多明尼克先生收我为弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马 马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上要生了 莎特拉太太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的雨 没法带去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跑一趟把医生叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸马上就会把医生带来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一下 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说忍… 但是要生的时候还是会生出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 没有医生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们自己来做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有接生的经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也没有犹豫的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家协力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来接生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德和阿尔去烧热水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮娘把所有的毛巾找来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 理多尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有消毒用的酒精
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓库里应该有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 把饮用水放在莎特拉太太的枕边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她来做不会有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是在医生之家出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小就把家里的医学书当画册一样看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说 没有真正学过？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计只是记得一个大概的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在只有依靠她的知识和胆量了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧开水 消毒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来 快想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮娘 你进来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键的时候 我是多么地无力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 痛 痛 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（怕 怕 怕）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不存在神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有现在 拜托他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血 血…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出 出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 真的出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 厉害 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 厉害地叫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只有那种小孩子一样的感想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这可是生命的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链金术师研究了几百年还没有成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类制造人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把生命的神秘和链金术做比较
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 是我的职业病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 孩子平安地出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后还有要我做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我拉起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（腰软了）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让比自己矮的男孩子背 真是耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说就把你扔地上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷看了银怀表里的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行打开的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都没让阿尔看过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对自己的警告和觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真是没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天的事情 必须要用这种形式带在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是你在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是你在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们兄弟俩都不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我代替你们哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是回乡下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆一个人会寂寞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为看到了爱德的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不能只抱着半吊子的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不需要连你也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要进一步加强自己的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你用上更好的机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了爱德能安心地继续旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我再次去求多明尼克先生收我为弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理多尔先生想让你过去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 快点把怀表还给我 你这小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不需要用右手打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用左手再打一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爷爷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色完全变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（娇宠 娇宠）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母子的健康状况良好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产后的处理也很适当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接生这种事 连大人也会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我已经拚命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是受大伙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么郑重的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没招了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（灵机一动）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 现在就收个弟子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个和那个是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不收弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无论如何都想做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以给你介绍一个住在山脚下的好技师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔来参观你的工作 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔来看看我的孙子 那倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的野丫头也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错过这班的话 下趟去达普利斯的就是三天后了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万事小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给婆婆打电话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好偷学那个老头子的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次见面的时候给我装个更好的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在师傅居住的城市 达普利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年们回想起修行的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是走向真理的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.19,0:24:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第12话 一即是全 全即是一
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.13,0:24:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹豫的言语
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为想保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}不必消去这份记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:35.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}人生不是还很漫长？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}那些没有做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:42.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}只是想重新做起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:58.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}明明一直在追赶着梦的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:05.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}跌跌撞撞地走在弯曲的小道上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:08.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}不奢望回到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:11.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}只是在苦寻那片丢失的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:13.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}就像你明白一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:18.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}除去那像牺牲之后的悲伤表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:20.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}罪孽之后并不是泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:21.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}而是一直以来背负的苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}迷失在没有出口的情感迷宫中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}在等待着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:27.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}就像在白色笔记本上刻画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:28.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}很想诚实地说出心声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}在逃避什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:32.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}…原来是叫做现实的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:35.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}为了实现愿望而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:38.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}不禁想要大喊  你能听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:43.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}平安无事却让人没法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:45.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}…无家可归
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:49.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}感谢同伴们带来的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:51.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以要更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.47,0:01:57.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur6}这种痛苦也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:32.97,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:38.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:44.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}约定和契约  被初夏的微风所怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:48.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人互相依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:57.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在强颜欢笑的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:02.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}隐藏着逐渐扩大的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:12.06,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以  只装做没有发现  选择了重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:21.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}在桌边继续等待那没有震撼的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:29.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在空白的夜里  无法迎接的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:34.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}其实我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.69,0:23:40.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.32,0:23:45.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}总有一天会想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:51.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}抱着没有实现的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.08,0:23:55.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人一起出发
